SUMMARY:Little Farm + Merry-Go-Round\, Tilden Park — Berkeley
DESCRIPTION:Hand-feed lettuce and celery to cows\, goats\, and sheep at t
 he free Little Farm — a classic toddler milestone — then a first spin on 
