SUMMARY:Berry Picking at Gizdich Ranch — Watsonville
DESCRIPTION:Pick-your-own olallieberries from low\, toddler-height bushes
  — the joy of plucking a berry and eating it on the spot. Open space to r
 oam and a famous pie shop to finish. Relaxed holiday-weekend pace.\nDrive
 : ~1 hr 15 min from Fremont
LOCATION:Gizdich Ranch Watsonville CA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
