SUMMARY:Lindsay Wildlife Experience — Walnut Creek
DESCRIPTION:A small\, easy wildlife museum where toddlers meet live rescu
 ed animals — hawks\, owls\, a rabbit — just feet away\, plus a hands-on n
 ature nook. Indoor and cool for a warm inland weekend.\nDrive: ~35 min fr
 om Fremont
