DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260727
SUMMARY:Emerald Glen Park Splash Pad — Dublin
DESCRIPTION:A big\, flat\, zero-depth splash pad with gentle fountains an
 d jets — the perfect first water-play experience for unsteady little feet
 . Bring a towel\, a swim diaper\, and let them squeal. Shady playground a
 longside.\nDrive: ~25 min from Fremont
LOCATION:Emerald Glen Park Dublin CA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
