DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260817
SUMMARY:Henry Cowell Redwoods State Park — Felton
DESCRIPTION:The flat\, stroller-friendly Redwood Grove Loop lets toddlers
  crane their necks at towering ancient redwoods\, touch the soft bark\, a
 nd toddle over a wide\, easy path. A calm\, awe-filled first nature walk.
 \nDrive: ~50 min from Fremont
LOCATION:Henry Cowell Redwoods State Park Felton CA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
