SUMMARY:Fairytale Town — Sacramento
DESCRIPTION:A storybook play park with climb-in nursery-rhyme sets — a gi
 ant boot slide\, a crooked house — plus gentle farm animals\, all scaled 
 for little legs. Shady\, gated\, and easy to navigate with a stroller.\nD
 rive: ~2 hrs from Fremont
LOCATION:Fairytale Town Sacramento CA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
